com.client.core.base.workflow.traversing

Interface Traverser

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ScheduledTasksTraverser<T>, ValidationTraverser
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractScheduledTasksTraverser, AbstractValidationTraverser, AppointmentEventTraverser, CandidateEducationEventTraverser, CandidateEventTraverser, CandidateReferenceEventTraverser, CandidateValidationTraverser, CandidateWorkHistoryEventTraverser, ClientContactEventTraverser, ClientContactValidationTraverser, ClientCorporationEventTraverser, ClientCorporationValidationTraverser, CorporateUserEventTraverser, JobEventTraverser, JobSubmissionEventTraverser, JobSubmissionValidationTraverser, JobValidationTraverser, NoteEventTraverser, NoteValidationTraverser, PlacementChangeRequestEventTraverser, PlacementChangeRequestValidationTraverser, PlacementCommissionEventTraverser, PlacementEventTraverser, PlacementValidationTraverser, SendoutEventTraverser, TaskEventTraverser

    public interface Traverser

    Unparameterized interface to represent a wrapper of event information to be passed through a workflow.

    This class exists so other generic classes (such as Node) can interact with the various kinds of Traversers without knowing about event-specific or entity-specific information.
